<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:13:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>跳水——中国选手谢勇夺得男子三米板金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-xie-wins-mens-three-metre-springboard-gold-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，中国选手谢思毅在巴黎奥运会男子三米板跳水比赛中获得金牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:33:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-xie-wins-mens-three-metre-springboard-gold-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国因强迫维吾尔人劳动而禁止另外五家中国公司进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/society-equity/us-bans-imports-five-more-chinese-companies-over-uyghurs-2024-08-08/</link><description>据政府发布的消息称，美国周四因涉嫌侵犯维吾尔人人权而禁止另外五家中国公司进口产品，这是其从美国供应链中消除强迫劳动制造的商品的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:38:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/society-equity/us-bans-imports-five-more-chinese-companies-over-uyghurs-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪推出首款配备激光雷达传感器的车型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-ev-maker-byd-launches-first-model-with-lidar-sensor-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国电动汽车（EV）巨头比亚迪周四推出了新版Seal EV，这是该公司首款配备激光雷达传感器的车型。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-ev-maker-byd-launches-first-model-with-lidar-sensor-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国明阳签署意大利风力涡轮机工厂协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-mingyang-signs-italy-wind-turbine-plant-deal-2024-08-08/</link><description>意大利工业部周四表示，中国明阳智能能源公司、意大利能源公司Renexia和意大利工业部已签署建立风力涡轮机制造厂的协议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-mingyang-signs-italy-wind-turbine-plant-deal-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>皮划艇-卡林顿领先新西兰四人夺得皮划艇金牌，德国队赢得男子比赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-carrington-leads-new-zealand-four-kayak-gold-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，新西兰选手丽莎·卡林顿 (Lisa Carrington) 率领女子皮划艇四名队员在马恩河畔韦尔斯航海体育场 (Vaires-sur-Marne Nautical Stadium) 夺得金牌，以另一场令人惊叹的表现，将她个人的奥运金牌数增加到六枚金牌和一枚铜牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-carrington-leads-new-zealand-four-kayak-gold-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>皮划艇——新西兰在巴黎奥运会女子皮划艇四人组500米决赛中夺得金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-new-zealand-win-gold-womens-kayak-four-500m-final-paris-olympics-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，新西兰在马恩河畔瓦雷斯航海体育场举行的女子皮划艇四人组 500 米决赛中获得奥运会金牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:50:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-new-zealand-win-gold-womens-kayak-four-500m-final-paris-olympics-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>英国航空将于 10 月 26 日起停止飞往北京的航班</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/british-airways-halt-flights-beijing-oct-26-2024-08-08/</link><description>英国航空公司周四表示，由于欧洲航空公司因禁止飞越俄罗斯领空而苦苦挣扎，该公司将于 10 月 26 日至 2025 年 11 月期间停止飞往北京的航班，但未详细说明原因。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/british-airways-halt-flights-beijing-oct-26-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>巴黎奥运会皮划艇——中国队夺得男子皮划艇双人500米金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-china-win-gold-mens-canoe-double-500m-paris-olympics-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，中国队在马恩河畔瓦雷斯航海体育场举行的男子皮划艇双人500米比赛中获得奥运会金牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:46:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-china-win-gold-mens-canoe-double-500m-paris-olympics-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>礼来公司将销售额预测上调 30 亿美元，减肥药效果显着</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/eli-lilly-raises-annual-profit-forecast-zepbound-quarterly-sales-cross-1-billion-2024-08-08/</link><description>礼来公司备受追捧的减肥药 Zepbound 的生产能力提高，促使该公司周四将年销售额预期提高 30 亿美元，股价上涨 13%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:51:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/eli-lilly-raises-annual-profit-forecast-zepbound-quarterly-sales-cross-1-billion-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场依然坎坷，等待就业现实检验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>尽管利润大幅下滑，中国芯片制造商中芯国际第二季度业绩仍超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/smic-posts-59-fall-q2-profit-yet-beats-expectations-2024-08-08/</link><description>中芯国际周四公布第二季度净利润下降 59.1%，尽管这家中国最大的芯片代工厂的业绩超出预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/smic-posts-59-fall-q2-profit-yet-beats-expectations-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院推迟中国开发商世茂的清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-court-adjourns-chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-petition-2024-08-08/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商世茂集团周四表示，香港法院已将针对该公司的清盘申请推迟至12月16日，从而使世茂有更多时间与债权人就修订后的重组方案进行合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 08:45:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-court-adjourns-chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-petition-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车市场达到里程碑，电动汽车和混合动力汽车占七月销量的一半</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-extend-declines-fourth-month-2024-08-08/</link><description>行业数据显示，7月份中国销售的所有汽车中有一半是新型纯电动汽车（EV）或插电式混合动力汽车，这一里程碑凸显了全球最大汽车市场在电动汽车采用方面远远领先于西方同行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 08:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-extend-declines-fourth-month-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国公布首例高温中暑死亡病例</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-discloses-first-heat-stroke-fatalities-amid-record-temperatures-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国东部沿海地区的气温连续第八天徘徊在 40 摄氏度（104 华氏度）左右，中国一座城市至少有两人因中暑死亡，还有更多人患病。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 07:18:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-discloses-first-heat-stroke-fatalities-amid-record-temperatures-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲航运公司将美国政治和中国经济视为航运势头面临的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/euronav-flags-us-politics-chinas-economy-risks-shipping-momentum-2024-08-08/</link><description>比利时油轮公司Euronav周四表示，预计红海航运改道将推动今年全球海上贸易增长，尽管美国总统更迭和中国经济放缓是风险因素。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/euronav-flags-us-politics-chinas-economy-risks-shipping-momentum-2024-08-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>